        <p>
            <strong> Thanks Mom for spoiling me in the past. </strong>
        </p>
        <p> Today I wanted to visit another area of the city that I haven't been to yet. So I got two bottles of water and set off. The route was less than 3 km long, but the sun was burning quite intensely again. I had chosen the Hayahay Treehouse Bar as my destination. From there, you have a nice view over the water and can see 3 neighboring islands. When I arrived at my destination, I had finished the now warm water and first needed a mango shake and a Sprite to cool down again. I stayed there in the shade for a while and enjoyed the view from the treehouse. Unfortunately, I had to admit that I'm getting really old. Not even an hour in the sun and I'm ready for an afternoon nap? I think I'm getting old!!!! </p>
